{"title_page": "Emilio Yam\u00edn", "text_new": "{{short description|Mexian-Lebanese footballer}}\n{{Spanish name|Yam\u00edn|Faure}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Emilio Yam\u00edn\n| image = \n| image_size =\n| fullname = Emilio Yam\u00edn Faure\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1993|03|31|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Toluca]], Mexico\n| height = 1.87 m\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Centre-back]]\n| currentclub = [[Salam Zgharta FC|Salam Zgharta]]\n| clubnumber =\n| youthyears1 = {{0|0000}}\u20132011\n| youthclubs1 = [[Deportivo Toluca F.C. Reserves and Academy|Toluca]]\n| youthyears2 = 2015\n| youthclubs2 = [[Club Puebla Reserves and Academy|Puebla]]\n| years1 = 2011\u20132018 | clubs1 = [[Deportivo Toluca F.C. Premier|Toluca Premier]]   | caps1 = 1 | goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2013      | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Jammerbugt FC|Jammerbugt]] (loan)              | caps2 =   | goals2 = \n| years3 = 2014      | clubs3 = \u2192 [[Club Puebla Premier|Puebla FC Premier]] (loan) | caps3 = 2 | goals3 = 0\n| years4 = 2014\u20132015 | clubs4 = \u2192 [[Potros UAEM]] (loan)                           | caps4 = 4 | goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2015\u20132016 | clubs5 = \u2192 [[Puebla FC]] (loan)                             | caps5 = 2 | goals5 = 0\n| years6 = 2017\u20132018 | clubs6 = \u2192 [[Potros UAEM]] (loan)                           | caps6 = 0 | goals6 = 0\n| years7 = 2018      | clubs7 = [[Salam Zgharta FC|Salam Zgharta]]                 | caps7 = 0 | goals7 = 0\n| pcupdate = 7 July 2018\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Emilio Yam\u00edn Faure''' ({{lang-ar|\u0627\u0645\u064a\u0644\u064a\u0648 \u064a\u0645\u064a\u0646}}; born 13 March 1993) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who last played as a [[Defender (association football)|centre-back]] for {{Lebanese football updater|SAL}} club [[Salam Zgharta FC|Salam Zgharta]]. Born in Mexico, Yam\u00edn obtained Lebanese citizenship through his origins.\n\n==Club career==\nYam\u00edn joined [[Lebanese Premier League]] club [[Salam Zgharta FC|Salam Zgharta]] on July 2018 on a one-year contract, alongside [[Alfredo Juraidini]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.record.com.mx/futbol-futbol-internacional-mexicanos-en-el-extranjero/dos-mexicanos-militaran-en-el-futbol-libanes|title=Dos mexicanos militar\u00e1n en el futbol liban\u00e9s|last=ircoronado|date=2018-07-14|website=www.record.com.mx|language=es|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sportsnewslb.com/%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b3%d9%84%d8%a7%d9%85-%d8%b2%d8%ba%d8%b1%d8%aa%d8%a7-%d8%b6%d9%85-%d9%84%d8%a7%d8%b9%d8%a8%d9%8a%d9%86-%d9%85%d9%83%d8%b3%d9%8a%d9%83%d9%8a%d9%8a%d9%86-%d9%85%d9%86-%d8%a7%d8%b5%d9%84/|title=\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0632\u063a\u0631\u062a\u0627 \u0636\u0645 \u0644\u0627\u0639\u0628\u064a\u0646 \u0645\u0643\u0633\u064a\u0643\u064a\u064a\u0646 \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0635\u0644 \u0644\u0628\u0646\u0627\u0646\u064a \u0644\u0635\u0641\u0648\u0641\u0647|date=2018-07-08|website=Sports News LB|language=ar|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|329725}}\n* {{Liga MX player|76288/emilio-yamin-faure}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Yamin, Emilio}}\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Toluca]]\n[[Category:Mexican footballers]]\n[[Category:Lebanese footballers]]\n[[Category:Mexican people of Lebanese descent]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Lebanese Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Salam Zgharta FC players]]\n\n\n{{Spain-footy-defender-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Mexian-Lebanese footballer}}\n{{Spanish name|Yam\u00edn|Faure}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Emilio Yam\u00edn\n| image = \n| image_size =\n| fullname = Emilio Yam\u00edn Faure\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1993|03|31|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Toluca]], Mexico\n| height = 1.87 m\n| position = [[Defender (