\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Male\n| 47\n| He travelled on the same plane with case #3.\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/al-patrulea-caz-de-coronavirus-confirmat-in-romania-1269577 |title=Al patrulea caz de coronavirus a fost confirmat \u00een Rom\u00e2nia |date=3 March 2020 |website=Digi24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305082643/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/al-patrulea-caz-de-coronavirus-confirmat-in-romania-1269577 |archive-date=5 March 2020 |access-date=3 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! 5\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 4 Mar.\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"tion\" />\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Male\n| 16\n| Nephew of case #4.\n| rowspan=\"2\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/5-cazuri-de-coronavirus-confirmate-in-romania-1270242 |title=6 cazuri de coronavirus confirmate \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. 2 pacien\u021bi testa\u021bi pozitiv ast\u0103zi |date=4 March 2020 |website=Digi24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200309191018/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/5-cazuri-de-coronavirus-confirmate-in-romania-1270242 |archive-date=9 March 2020 |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! 6\n| {{Failure|Hospitalised}}\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Suceava County|Suceava]]\n| Male\n| 71\n| Moved to intensive care on 18 March; comorbid lymphoma.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ziaruldeiasi.ro/stiri/covid-19-la-iasi-primele-probleme-grave-doi-pacienti-la-ati-lipsuri-materiale-in-spitale--247192.html |title=COVID-19 la Ia\u015fi: primele probleme grave. Doi pacien\u021bi la ATI, lipsuri materiale \u00een spitale |date=19 March 2020 |website=Ziarul de Iasi}}</ref>\n|-\n! 7\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 6 Mar.\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"tion\" />\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Female\n| 16\n| Classmate of case #5.\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esent